{"tid":707330,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"絲入) 如果男朋友窮到要住劏房...你會點?","createTime":"2018-06-18T14:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T05:37:48.000Z","uid":82845,"like":11,"dislike":198,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e02736901094f56072c6f27f50070af5ec9f03","tid":707330,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"男朋友窮我就不嬲都知既..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢一早講過自己唔有錢..佢屋企父母又早離婚..無咩野留到俾佢..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢由中學到大學都係靠自己一手一腳搵錢返黎...到而家出黎社會都係靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好尊敬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我當我每次講到住邊時...佢都唔肯講...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來我終於得知佢原來係深水埗果d好雜好混亂既劏房&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連張梳化都冇...<br />\n我真係無諗過佢真係會窮成咁..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似無咩將來可言...而家我好混亂...唔知應唔應該繼續同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩臭雞食屎啦果d垃圾留言就可以上一頁出返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只限絲留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4597dbbf8ece3776a2504b38d9c743df6bc63f56","tid":707330,"uid":137374,"like":123,"dislike":5,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"64e2b09c616924dc8878d593e107d2cd074c3b77","tid":707330,"uid":44840,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n現今社會兩個人都有返工<br />\n一齊租間屋都唔算得係咩問題<br />\n<br />\n睇你會唔會陪佢一齊過世囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a45d5dad15d78be028a7813c6a43ca64fbcaf0","tid":707330,"uid":52062,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18